CICD is Continuous Integration and Continuous Deployment/Continuous Delivery

CI is a process to integrate multiple tools or processes before deploying to customer
CD is a process of delivering/deploying to the customer with coninuous improvement.

unit testing,code build, static code analysis, code quality/ vulnerability, Automation testing[performance +Regression + END2END testing], Reports, Deployment is common process to delivering product.

the way to automating above things is a CICD process.


e.g. jenkins is a orcehestrator tool, by using pipelines, github actions
Pipeline consists of Build, test, reporting, containerizing, security analysis, deployment.


# ############################################################
# usual process of deployment of a product
#  
# App development --> SVC --> jenking  --> ENV[Dev + staging + Production]
